My Own Private Idaho;;80;;79;;R;;In this loose adaptation of Shakespeare's "Henry IV," Mike Waters (River Phoenix) is a gay hustler afflicted with narcolepsy. Scott Favor (Keanu Reeves) is the rebellious son of a mayor. Together, the two travel from Portland, Oregon to Idaho and finally to the coast of Italy in a quest to find Mike's estranged mother. Along the way they turn tricks for money and drugs, eventually attracting the attention of a wealthy benefactor and sexual deviant.;;Lgbtq+,Drama;;Gus Van Sant;;1991;;River Phoenix,Keanu Reeves,James Russo,William Richert,Rodney Harvey,Chiara Caselli,Michael Parker,Jessie Thomas,Flea,Grace Zabriskie;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/my_own_private_idaho